# Luz Spectrum Analyzer
# =====================
#
# NOTE: the program pavucontrol can be used to change the Spectrum Analyzer's sound source: mics, or listening to the playing music ("Monitor of ...")
#
# To build Spectrum Analyzer on Ubuntu use:

sudo apt-get install build-essential libasound2-dev libfftw3-dev liblo-dev libgtkmm-2.4-dev libgtkglextmm-x11-1.2-dev libgl1-mesa-dev libglu1-mesa-dev
make
